  "original_title": "\u0db8\u0ddd\u0da7\u0dbb\u0dca \u0dbb\u0dae - \u0dba\u0dad\u0dd4\u0dbb\u0dd4\u0db4\u0dd0\u0daf\u0dd2 \u0d9c\u0dd0\u0da7\u0dd3 03\u0d9a\u0da7 \u0db6\u0dbb\u0db4\u0dad\u0dbd\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "03 serious in car-motorcycle collision",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "According to the police, three members of the same family, including a small child who was traveling on the motorcycle, were seriously injured yesterday (04th) evening when a car collided with a motorcycle in the Siruppiddy area of \u200b\u200bJaffna Chhalweli police domain.",
        "Preliminary investigations have revealed that the car which was traveling from Pedurutuduwa to Jaffna lost control of its speed and collided with a motorcycle which was running on the road.",
        "When an 8-year-old child who was traveling on a motorcycle and the child's mother and father were seriously injured in the accident, local residents took steps to admit them to the Jaffna Teaching Hospital.",
        "After the accident, there was a heated situation between the local residents and the driver of the car, and the police officers who went to the spot took steps to arrest the driver of the car.",
        "The police, who are conducting the investigation, added that the car driver's careless driving is suspected to be the cause of the accident."
      ],
